                </h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
                    {
                        [
                            {
                                label: "Grading-Focused Students",
                                body: "You want to go into your next grading feeling completely prepared. We will make sure your pattern is clean, confident, and examiner-ready.",
                            },
                            {
                                label: "Pattern Enthusiasts",
                                body: "You love the artistry of Taekwondo and want to go deep on technique. Poomsae class is your space to pursue that interest with like-minded practitioners.",
                            },
                            {
